name: Serie Tribute: 01 - Harley Quinn
description: This new series #Tribute has a collectible card format. It will make a tribute tour about superheroes and villains. A new creative venture of Roboto Inc. for its great collectors. Prototypes designed by Norma Xelda Jara. Let's have fun! They don't collect dirt on the shelf and don't take up space ideal for your cell phone or computer!
